<!-- ================= SEMANTIC OVERVIEW (SEO BOOSTER) ================= -->
<section class="section section--lighter section--semantic">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <p>
      VAIRA Technology is a Swiss deep‑tech consultancy specializing in engineering, industrialization, 
      and the development of reliable, scalable technologies. We help organizations move from early 
      concept to industrial performance by combining technical depth with architectural clarity - 
      ensuring solutions that are intentional, robust, and ready for real‑world operation in industrial environments.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= INTRODUCTION ================= -->
<section class="section section--lighter">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <h2>Practical Technology Expertise</h2>
    <p>
      <strong>Innovation creates potential.</strong><br>
      <strong>Industrialization turns it into value.</strong>
    </p>
    
    <p>
      VAIRA works at the intersection of technology, engineering, and manufacturing. We help organizations bridge the gap between technical feasibility and scalable, industrial reality.
    </p>
    
    <p>
      Our focus is practical: technologies that work, processes that scale, and decisions grounded in engineering understanding.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= CORE CAPABILITIES ================= -->
<section class="section" id="what-we-do">
  <div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="split">

      <div class="split-left">
        <h2>Core Capabilities</h2>

        <div class="split-body">
         
          <h3>Technology & Process Development</h3>
          <p>Structured development of products and production processes, from early validation to robust industrial design.</p>

          <h3>Industrialization & Scale-Up</h3>
          <p>Translating prototypes into stable, repeatable, and economically viable manufacturing solutions.</p>

          <h3>Innovation Strategy & Technology Assessment</h3>
          <p>Clear evaluation of technical opportunities, risks, and maturity – enabling informed strategic decisions.</p>

          <h3>Technical Due Diligence</h3>
          <p>Independent assessment of deep-tech ventures and industrial technologies, grounded in operational experience.</p>

          <h3>Startup & Venture Support</h3>
          <p>Hands-on guidance for deep-tech founders and corporate ventures navigating development and industrial scale-up.</p>
          
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="split-right">
