<!-- ================= WHY VAIRA ================= -->
<section id="why-vaira" class="section">
  <div class="content-wrapper wrapper--narrow">
    <h2>Why VAIRA</h2>

    <p>
      Our approach is shaped by founder‑operator experience, deep‑tech focus and practical work in 
      industrial environments. We aim for solutions that are technically sound, realistic to implement 
      and reliable in operation.
    </p>

    <div class="why-grid">

      <div class="feature-block">
        <div class="feature-block-icon"></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Founder‑Operator Perspective</h3>
          <p>
            VAIRA was founded by Dr. Raphael Heeb, co‑founder and former CEO of NEMATX AG, an ETH Zurich 
            spin‑off developing high‑performance additive manufacturing / 3D printing systems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-block">
        <div class="feature-block-icon"></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Collaborative Approach</h3>
          <p>
            We work directly with engineering teams, operations and suppliers to understand constraints, 
            resolve issues and ensure solutions function in real conditions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-block">
        <div class="feature-block-icon"></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Engineering Depth</h3>
          <p>
            Our work sits at the intersection of materials, hardware, processes and production – often 
            in environments with high complexity and non-trivial scale‑up challenges.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-block">
        <div class="feature-block-icon"></div>
        <div>
          <h3>Senior‑Only Delivery</h3>
          <p>
            All work is carried out by senior expertise, ensuring continuity, in-depth technical knowledge and effective 
            transfer of know‑how.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

